<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Document Preparation</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Preparing your document for the document authentication and legalization process can involve multiple steps including notarization, translation, and more.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="https://idc.local/our-apostille-services/document-apostille/canadian-document-apostille/preparing-documents-for-apostille/" type="page" id="34548">Prepare your documents</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></article>
<!-- /wp:group -->

