<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Document Legalization</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The document legalization process is the last step of the process and involves having your document legalized by the embassy or consulate of the destination country.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="https://idc.local/our-apostille-services/document-authentication-legalization/document-legalization/" type="page" id="34553">Get official recognition</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></article>
